data.description: Welcome home to Boulder Springs! Less than a year old, The Montego by Aruba homes features 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and SO much storage space! With soaring ceilings and tasteful finishes, this ranch home is the entertainer's dream! A true wide open floor plan with naturally lit living and beautiful kitchen space, while also having the option for a theater space, game room, or whatever your heart desires in the massive finished basement! Step out onto the covered patio and enjoy the view of nature that this home backs up to. You truly cannot build this home brand new for this price!   *This home is being sold as-is, inspections welcome*
